{"tid":2478781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港以前係喺澳洲嘅 “sphere of influence”，大概冇乜人留意到。","createTime":"2021-04-07T10:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T10:10:30.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bd83dfc6a1be2e45ca8916773ef567ac17814f","tid":2478781,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2996188510617220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2996188510617220&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=407959d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2996188510617220</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n香港以前係喺澳洲嘅 &ldquo;sphere of influence&rdquo;，大概冇乜人留意到。八九十年代香港嘅鬼佬公務員澳洲人多過英國人，大概冇人會研究。李澤楷同 News Corp 嘅 deal，大概都冇人記得。澳洲投資、貿易對中國「脫貧」嘅「貢獻」遠遠超出美國，大概都被視為理所當然。"}]}